{
  "texts": [
    "It is evident that EarthGPT provides accurate, detailed, and diverse descriptions of RS images.",
    "D. Visual Question AnsweringThe evaluation of VQA is also divided into supervised and zero-shot assessments.",
    "For the supervised VQA setting, we adopt the test set of CRSVQA including 1000 imagequestion-answer pairs.",
    "Following the setting of MQVQA, 10% of image-question-answer pairs are adopted as the test set, and the overall accuracy (OA) is reported.",
    "For zero-shot VQA setting, RSVQA-HR is utilized to evaluate the performance of EarthGPT and other MLLMs."
  ]
}